# Project stack

- **Svelte 5** with runes mode (forced in `vite.config.ts` except `node_modules`)
- **SvelteKit 2** (`@sveltejs/kit@next`, config in `vite.config.ts` via `sveltekit()` plugin)
- **Tailwind CSS 4** + **daisyUI 5** (configure in `src/routes/layout.css`)
- **Drizzle ORM** + Postgres via `pg` (`src/lib/server/db/`)
- **Better Auth** (`src/lib/server/auth.ts`, `hooks.server.ts`)
- **Zod** for runtime validation of forms, actions, and API input
- **uuid** for client-facing IDs (prefer `crypto.randomUUID()` on server when possible)

## Conventions

- Server-only code lives in `src/lib/server/` or `+page.server.ts` / `+server.ts`
- Env vars: `src/env.ts` with `defineEnvVars`; import from `$app/env/private` or `$app/env/public`
- i18n: Paraglide (`$lib/paraglide/`)
- Use `$app/paths` `resolve()` for typed internal links
- Use `$app/state` `page` instead of deprecated `$app/stores`
- Prefer daisyUI component classes over hand-rolled Tailwind for UI primitives
- Form focus: default daisyUI field rings; joined inputs use `label.input` wrapper — see `daisyui5.mdc`
- Validate untrusted input with Zod before DB writes or auth calls
- UI icons: `@lucide/svelte` only — no inline `<svg>` or unicode arrows in components
- Page titles: `{page content} - {app name}` via `PageTitle` / `formatPageTitle` (see `page-titles.mdc`)
